nodes.text: The Quence sector was a sector located in the Outer Rim Territories near the Portmoak sector. Planets in Quence included Elshandruu Pica, Xiunsrus, Suarbi 7, and the Empartheca system. The sector was represented in the New Republic Senate by first Elegos A'Kla and then Releqy A'Kla.
Before 1 BBY, the Sullustan gambler Cunbus Locb visited several planets in this area, earned an amount of money, and left aboard his ship, Distant Wind, to the chagrin of several fleeced locals.
